br />\n一直都講緊衝擊係法理之外，但係情理之中<br />\n唔係乜嘢叫公民抗命？<br />\n<br />\n用乜鳩強姦嚟比喻，梗本唔恰當，我哋都可以比喻政權警權強姦我哋（完全無違和添）。<br />\nAnyway呢啲下三濫抹黑其實冇意思，po出嚟之前自己睇多次啦，作為一個成年人理應明辨是非，我喺佢就搵窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"e90134e4b4a793d2ec4849a4066425f96f10232f","tid":1288532,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T19:38:54.000Z","msg":"隻黑警有讀寫障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/HqW3bQA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqW3bQA.gif&h=219d0f9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f1db4432ef584ec6b2bc20fa9312e701f38675a","tid":1288532,"uid":192078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6df8a08d09fc25727fe2ecf534dcf8ca3ba9abd1","tid":1288532,"uid":228195,"like":262,"dislike":3,"score":259,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔明佢想表達乜野<br />\n好心就進修下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T19:43:03.000Z","msg":"我明～犬隻慣咗叫G 佢覺得放低$就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6bd31015989251811a23ab7e4b074d4667d273","tid":1288532,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T19:47:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25ac30858f6f8371b939a450fcf126de5d91bbb5","tid":1288532,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T19:47:30.000Z","msg":"畜牲真係畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想屌閪就屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340d800fa552ae5725a69f5e06ebae8ef14e7412"